===================================
Version 0.2.5.7
===================================
• Executions: Timeout to avoid scripts running forever

• Minor features:
  Queue observer: shows task running time
  Textile Output: Added table/blockquote styles
  Outputs: show additional info for root users

• Bug fixes:
  Suite execution status didn't show correctly as soon as it started running
  Deleting a Suite deletes its scheduled tasks
  Hide deleted cases from Script editor

===================================
Version 0.2.5.4
===================================
• Menu: Added access to admin functions through the main menu
• Execution Output: Added the ability to visualize the output of an execution in HTML format
• User Functions: Added search on all projects for the search function
• Adding rake task to refresh status for non finished executions
• Adding ruby blocks on cacique functions 

• Bug fixes:
* Solution for FF 9 and chrome compatibility: 
  You can create and edit relationships in a suite with these browsers
* Editor: Hightligthing bug fix when type '/'
* User Functions: The filter used in the search function is not reset when changing project
* History: Fixes the status percentage on execution history listings

===================================
Version 0.2.5.3
===================================
• Suites, scripts and data set:
  + Deletion implemented with "soft delete"
  + Execution history is preserved

• Logging when running WebDriver:
  + Adding driver user function
  + Refactoring selenium user function
  + Adding webdriver_stop user function

• Bug fixes:
* Javascript error when trying to save a function when it's created
* Removed parameter "execution_running" from the url of the script editor
* Migrations:
  Refactoring of the user function "finalize_run_script": 
    closed instances of Selenim or WebDriver that are open.
  Refactoring of the user function "webdriver_init": 
    Hub ip was changed by the constant HUB_IP
    Modified the url parameter name

